content: --फल (निष्फल) {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {1} bearing no fruit, fruitless (<ab>fig.</ab> also), unsuccessful; futile; निष्फलारंभयत्नाः <ls>Me. 54.</ls> {2} useless, profitless, vain; <ls>Ku. 4. 13.</ls> {3} barren (as a tree). {4} meaningless (as a word). {5} seedless, impotent. (--ला, --ली a woman past child-bearing.
